 <title>Video: Barcelona&#039;s Bizarre Human Statues</title>
 <link>http://www.theworldisnotflat.com/human-staues</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;You&amp;#39;ve likely seen the people who paint themselves silver and pose on a box to earn spare change.&amp;nbsp; The folks in Barcelona takes this whole idea to whole new level.&amp;nbsp; The creative, the absurd, the animated, the banal, it&amp;#39;s all there and it&amp;#39;s all just so weird.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;object height=&quot;350&quot; width=&quot;425&quot;&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;movie&quot; value=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/v/S8DuuWE9oXM&quot;&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;wmode&quot; value=&quot;transparent&quot;&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;embed src=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/v/S8DuuWE9oXM&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot; wmode=&quot;transparent&quot; height=&quot;350&quot; width=&quot;425&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;&lt;/object&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Correction:&amp;nbsp; In the video, I mention an article by a UK paper called the Guardian.&amp;nbsp; I meant to refer to &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4158/is_20061005/ai_n16760570&quot;&gt;this article&lt;/a&gt; in the Independent - not the Guardian.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;clear&quot; /&gt;</description>
